# Never copy host-installed dependencies into the build context. The Dockerfiles run
# their own `npm install` inside the (Linux) image; copying a host node_modules (esp.
# from Windows) bakes in wrong-platform binaries and duplicate package copies — e.g. a
# second React instance, which breaks hooks at runtime ("Invalid hook call").
node_modules
**/node_modules

# Build output (regenerated inside the image)
dist
**/dist

# Local-only
.git
.env
**/.env.local
